CBRE Gold Coast and Ray White Commercial (Gold Coast), as the joint exclusive agents, are
pleased to present 8 Bay Street, Southport Qld For Sale via Public Auction.

The property is a regular shaped 405m²* parcel of land situated in Bay Street, the heart of Southport's legal district. The two-storey building has approximately 333m²* of lettable area and already has an office fitout with lobby/reception area, board room, offices and bathroom facilities.

The property occupies a prime CBD location and is in within short walking distance of the Southport Court House, G:Link Station, St Hilda's Private Girls School and other inner city amenities.

Key features of this unique property:
- Freestanding freehold building ready to occupy
- 405m²* of land with 333m²* 2-level office building
- Secure parking for up to 8 vehicles
- Walking distance to St Hilda's school, major shops & businesses and G:Link station
- Sensational Southport CBD location, just around the corner from the Court House
- Deceased estate auction - don't miss out!

*Approximately

Auction: Thursday, 19th August 2021 at 11am
Gold Coast Turf Club, Bundall

For a copy of the Information Memorandum or to arrange an inspection of the property, please do not hesitate to contact the exclusive marketing agents.
